# Download Android source with local_manifests
 Refer to http://source.android.com/source/downloading.html

 $ repo init -u git://github.com/LineageOS/android.git -b lineage-17.1
 $ git clone git@github.com:realme-trinket-organization/local_manifests.git .repo/local_manifests -b lineage-17.1
 $ repo sync

 Don't forget to clone your kernel source to kernel/realme/sm6125
